                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5917" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0891</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9273 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值共创：RMW媒体融合电商扶贫之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Value Co-creation: RMW Company’s Integration of E-commerce and Poverty Alleviation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纪宇，徐扬，马健，周宁，邹艳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京航空航天大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人民网股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新闻出版业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值共创；价值链；生态圈；电商扶贫；脱贫攻坚；2021百优案例；精准扶贫与企业社会责任专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">value co-creation; value chain; ecosystem; e-commerce poverty alleviation; poverty alleviation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年是我国脱贫攻坚的决胜之年和收官之年，然而2019年底在全球范围内爆发的新冠肺炎疫情对我国农村地区的农副产品生产销售造成了巨大冲击。本案例通过描述RMW媒体在疫情背景下参与电商助农扶贫的实践过程，着重分析媒体融合对电商价值链的赋能维度与要素，并基于价值链剖析直播带货模式推广的局限性，在此基础上通过引入国家互联网营销师培训与地方政府、头部电商平台和农户深度合作构建多方共赢的电商生态圈，帮助农户在危机下解决农副产品滞销问题起到关键作用，进一步探索了媒体在助农扶贫中寻求社会效益与经济效益兼顾实现价值共创的实践机理。本案例对正在进行农村扶贫项目推广的传统媒体、开发农村电商经济新模式的互联网企业或致力于发展农村电商和多元化经济的地方政府，如何以农村电商价值链赋能为切入点引领和带动传统媒体、地方政府、电商平台和农户的有机融合与发展，让价值共创的生态圈思维在企业战略管理和决策方面成为驱动价值创造的底层逻辑具有较好的启示和借鉴作用。同时，对学生从理论和实践相结合的角度理解基于生态圈的价值共创、价值链赋能的作用机制提供有益帮助。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">2020 is the year of decisive victory and the final year for my country&#39;s poverty alleviation. However, the global outbreak of the new crown pneumonia epidemic at the end of 2019 has had a huge impact on the production and sales of agricultural and sideline products in rural areas of my country. This case describes the practical process of RMW media participating in e-commerce poverty alleviation in the context of the epidemic, focusing on the analysis of the empowerment dimensions and elements of media integration to the e-commerce value chain, and analyzes the limitations of the promotion of the live delivery model based on the value chain. On this basis, through the introduction of national Internet marketer training, in-depth cooperation with local governments, leading e-commerce platforms and farmers to build a win-win e-commerce ecosystem, helping farmers to solve the problem of unsalable agricultural and sideline products plays a key role in the crisis, and further Explored the practical mechanism of the media seeking social and economic benefits in helping farmers and poverty alleviation to achieve value co-creation. In this case, how to use rural e-commerce value chain empowerment as an entry point for traditional media that are promot-ing rural poverty alleviation projects, Internet companies developing new models of rural e-commerce economy, or local governments dedicated to the development of rural e-commerce and diversified economies Leading and driving the organic integration and devel-opment of traditional media, local governments, e-commerce platforms, and farmers, and making the ecosystem thinking of value co-creation become the underlying logic of driving value creation in corporate strategic management and decision-making has good enlighten-ment and reference. . At the same time, it provides useful help for students to understand the mechanism of value co-creation and value chain empowerment based on the ecosystem from the perspective of combining theory and practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">PEST分析；赋能理论；波特价值链模型；直播电商价值共创行为过程理论框架；价值共创生态圈模型；创造共享价值理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
